data.title: Planning and Zoning Department
data.meta_description: View the responsibilities of the department, access applications and forms, and browse maps and ordinances.
data.text:
Have you wondered what is being built near your neighborhood? Did you hear that business XYZ was coming to New Kent and you want to see what has been submitted to the County presently? Check out the Land Development Viewer! Click HERE for viewer instructions!

Planning to build? Check your setbacks for primary and accessory structures.

Are you planning on opening a new business in New Kent County? The Table of Land Uses will guide you to find out what is permitted in your zoning and then you can submit a Zoning Permit Application prior to obtaining a Business License.

Find out what your property is zoned in the GIS under "Vision".
